---

## Quickstart
### Requirements
- Docker + Docker Compose
- IronPython 4 installed if running manually

### Running
```bash
make all       # Build Rust backend
make run       # Run Rust server (http://localhost:8080)
make agi       # Start FastAPI AGI (http://localhost:8000)
make rake      # Trigger AGI ritual using Ruby
```

### Docker
```bash
docker compose up --build
```

---

## API Endpoints
